ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectLaura Speakman Remission Order
PrecisINDIVIDUAL REMISSION ORDER remits penalties in the amounts of $11.20 and $19.16 for the 1995 and 1998 taxation years, respectively, and arrears interest in the amounts of $907.45, $2,852.15, $449.25, $683.10 and $131.91 for the 1992, 1993, 1995, 1997 and 1998 taxation years, respectively, and all interest on the penalties and interest, paid or payable under Part I of the Income Tax Act by LAURA SPEAKMAN.
